livingthing guard1 local trigger "Chris"
	if = guard1 locX 497
		if = guard1 locY 673
		set guard1 locxy 1 1
		chat trigger "Woah, trippy!  It looks like he just disappeared into a cloud of mushroom spores."
		chat trigger "**You think: Maybe I'm hallucinating this from all these spores but this might be the only way to find that guy again.  I better go kick that mushroom over there like he just did."
